&lt;p&gt;Detailed drawings/full particulars of the proposed development showing the matters set out below must be submitted to and approved by the Local Planning Authority, in writing, prior to commencement of the relevant part of works. The development shall not be carried out otherwise than in accordance with the details thus approved:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

a) 1:10 and 1:20 sections, plans and elevations of all windows.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
b) Details of materials to be used for the bike store located within the front garden.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
c) Details of the timber to be used to the front boundary treatment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;REASON: To ensure the proposed development integrates with the host building and surrounding conservation area.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
